{"tid":2151192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国人舉報台灣遊戲「辱华」  反遭Steam「送中」","createTime":"2020-08-11T09:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T22:17:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":77,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f21022e65a0ad9999a061b8bf8eb96c15b5c9b2b","tid":2151192,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"台灣獨立遊戲開發者「Leonard H」日前於steam平台上架《赤毒》（Red Virus），由於遊戲中的病毒長著「習近平」的臉，反派人物設計成中國外交部發言人和世衛秘書長譚德塞的模樣，讓中國「愛國」玩家怒向steam平台檢舉「辱華」，要求下架遊戲。不料，卻反被steam發現這名玩家改變ip位置，違規「跨區」到俄羅斯，於是「熱心」將他的帳號遣送回「中國」，讓網友笑翻「現在知道送中多可怕了吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3256760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3256760&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fiukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=2330ede0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3256760&h=7edc8872\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3256760</a>"},{"pid":"7640cd0fbfcfb0d8ae38c4aae3d1082a7fa5b992","tid":2151192,"uid":202878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f1479d365b74a1a01e4edc2e89a3ef3306d511","tid":2151192,"uid":36178,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遊戲中的病毒長著「習近平」的臉</blockquote><br />\njpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd0d077fe9a966d248030ef822a0cb7756a3d98","tid":2151192,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281a1789e5a5692b58eb2fcbe5935d8002ae8fde","tid":2151192,"uid":83602,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:28:42.000Z","msg":"班傻閪又話想靜靜地打機算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif